# Inference Modes — How Each Mode Works

Conceptual explanation of the 4 inference modes in this platform, how data flows, and when to use each.

---

## Overview

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[10 Models + Data] --> B{Choose Mode}
    B --> C[Single GPU]
    B --> D[Hybrid CPU+GPU]
    B --> E[Spark Distributed CPU]
    B --> F[Spark Distributed GPU]

    C --> G[42K samples/sec]
    D --> H[33K samples/sec]
    E --> I[3K samples/sec × N nodes]
    F --> J[5K samples/sec × N nodes]
```

