### Scaling (GPU Cluster)

- 1 GPU, 2 partitions: 5,329 samples/sec (measured)
- 7 GPUs, 14 partitions: ~37K samples/sec (projected, with MPS)
- 16 GPUs, 32 partitions: ~85K samples/sec (projected)

### Code Path

```
Same as Mode 3, with:
  SPARK_EXECUTOR_GPU=1 environment variable
  → infer_on_partition() picks device="cuda"
  → Each partition loads models on GPU and runs forward passes
```

