## How Modes Relate to Each Other

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[CUDAStreamsEngine] --> B[Single GPU Mode]
    A --> C[Hybrid Mode - GPU subset]
    D[ThreadPoolExecutor] --> C
    D --> E[Hybrid Mode - CPU subset]
    F[Spark RDD + Broadcast] --> G[Distributed CPU]
    F --> H[Distributed GPU]
    A -.->|"Used inside each executor<br>on real cluster"| H

    style A fill:#90EE90
    style F fill:#87CEEB
```

The `CUDAStreamsEngine` is the core building block — it's used directly in Single GPU mode, inside Hybrid mode for the GPU subset, and inside each Spark executor on a real GPU cluster.

